message:
(1) maybe you forgot the history, but the palestinians were just minding their own business when a bunch of jews came and stole their land from them and created a jewish-exclusive state on their heads. now the palestinians live in squalor and in refugee camps, and have no political rights. so it's pretty hard to blame the victim.

&amp;#x200B;

(2) you obviously know that the palestinains arent in control over the situation. they have been begging for a tiny proto-state for years, and have been rejected by israel. the fact is, israel doesnt want to give them anything, so they have nothing they can do.

&amp;#x200B;

(3) no state should be based on race or religion. so the way to solve the conflict is just to have one state where they all have the same rights to vote and equality.
